<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Perímetro — AI y Ciberseguridad</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,300&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:        #0a0c0f;
      --bg2:       #0f1218;
      --bg3:       #141820;
      --border:    #1e2530;
      --accent:    #00e5ff;
      --accent2:   #ff4444;
      --text:      #e8eaf0;
      --muted:     #5a6478;
      --muted2:    #8892a4;
      --tag-bg:    #0d1a20;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── GRAIN OVERLAY ── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* ── SCANLINE ── */
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 2px,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 999;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
      height: 60px;
      background: rgba(10,12,15,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--text);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted2);
    }

    .nav-links li a:hover { color: var(--accent); transition: color 0.2s; }

    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-subscribe {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bg);
      background: var(--accent);
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-subscribe:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      padding-top: 60px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* background grid lines */
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .hero-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 5rem 3rem 5rem 2.5rem;
      position: relative;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .hero-statement {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-statement p {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.2vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.25;
      color: var(--text);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .hero-statement em {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-style: normal;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 360px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .hero-meta .dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent2);
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.8); }
    }

    .hero-right {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 5rem 2.5rem 5rem 3rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .featured-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--accent2);
      padding-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    .featured-card {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .featured-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

    .featured-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), transparent);
    }

    .card-category {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .card-excerpt {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .card-footer {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .read-more {
      color: var(--accent);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      transition: gap 0.2s;
    }

    .featured-card:hover .read-more { gap: 0.7rem; }

    /* ── TICKER ── */
    .ticker-wrap {
      background: var(--accent);
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 36px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .ticker-track {
      display: flex;
      animation: ticker 30s linear infinite;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .ticker-item {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--bg);
      padding: 0 3rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .ticker-sep { opacity: 0.4; }

    @keyframes ticker {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ── MAIN GRID ── */
    .main-content {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    /* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .section-link {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ── ARTICLE LIST ── */
    .article-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

    .article-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .article-item:hover { background: var(--bg2); margin: 0 -1rem; padding: 1.75rem 1rem; }

    .article-num {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: var(--border);
      line-height: 1;
      align-self: start;
      padding-top: 4px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .article-item:hover .article-num { color: var(--accent); }

    .article-body {}

    .article-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      background: var(--tag-bg);
      color: var(--muted2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .tag.accent { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(0,229,255,0.05); }
    .tag.red { color: var(--accent2); border-color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(255,68,68,0.05); }

    .article-title {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .article-excerpt {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .article-meta {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    /* ── SIDEBAR ── */
    .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2.5rem; }

    .sidebar-widget {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg2);
    }

    .widget-header {
      padding: 0.9rem 1.25rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--muted2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .widget-header::before {
      content: '';
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      background: var(--accent);
    }

    /* radar widget */
    .radar-list { padding: 0.5rem 0; }

    .radar-item {
      padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }

    .radar-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .radar-item:hover { background: var(--bg3); }

    .radar-source {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .radar-title {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.4;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .radar-time {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    /* newsletter widget */
    .newsletter-body { padding: 1.25rem; }

    .newsletter-body p {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .newsletter-input {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      outline: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .newsletter-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
    .newsletter-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }

    .newsletter-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg);
      border: none;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .newsletter-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* about widget */
    .about-body {
      padding: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .about-avatar {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #0066ff);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--bg);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .about-name {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .about-bio {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ── ALERTA BANNER ── */
    .alerta-banner {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto 0;
      padding: 0 2.5rem;
    }

    .alerta-header-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .alerta-section-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .dot-red {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent2);
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }

    .alerta-ver-todas {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--accent2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .alerta-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.2);
    }

    .alerta-inner {
      background: rgba(255,68,68,0.05);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.15);
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .alerta-inner--dark {
      background: rgba(255,68,68,0.02);
    }

    .alerta-inner:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .alerta-badge {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .alerta-badge--defacement {
      color: var(--accent2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.4);
      background: rgba(255,68,68,0.08);
    }

    .alerta-badge--filtracion {
      color: #ffaa00;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,170,0,0.4);
      background: rgba(255,170,0,0.08);
    }

    .alerta-badge--darkforum {
      color: var(--muted2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }

    .alerta-text {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted2);
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .alerta-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 4rem;
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-note {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .hero-statement { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both; }
    .hero-sub       { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.15s ease both; }
    .hero-meta      { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both; }
    .featured-card  { animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">PERÍMETRO</div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#">Análisis</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Radar</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Alertas</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Glosario</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Acerca</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <button class="btn-subscribe">Suscribirse</button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-statement">
        <p><em>AI y Ciberseguridad</em> —<br>Lo que importa,<br>cuando importa.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-sub">Sigo de cerca el mundo de AI y ciberseguridad — y te cuento lo que encontré, lo que me preocupa, y lo que creo que importa para tu negocio.</div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span>Actualizado semanalmente</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="featured-label">— Análisis destacado</div>
      <div class="featured-card">
        <div class="card-category">AI Empresarial</div>
        <h2 class="card-title">¿Tu empresa necesita IA ahora mismo, o puede esperar?</h2>
        <p class="card-excerpt">
          Cada semana aparece una herramienta nueva que promete transformar tu negocio. La pregunta real no es si adoptar IA — es cuándo y para qué. Una guía práctica para decidir sin dejarse llevar por el ruido.
        </p>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <span>12 mayo 2025 · 6 min lectura</span>
          <span class="read-more">Leer análisis →</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TICKER -->
  <div class="ticker-wrap">
    <div class="ticker-track">
      <div class="ticker-item">
        <span>Radar semanal disponible</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Nueva vulnerabilidad en routers domésticos afecta a PYMES</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Microsoft Copilot: qué puede hacer realmente por tu empresa</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Phishing en México creció 43% en el último trimestre</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Guía: cómo proteger tu correo empresarial sin gastar de más</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
      </div>
      <!-- duplicate for infinite scroll -->
      <div class="ticker-item">
        <span>Radar semanal disponible</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Nueva vulnerabilidad en routers domésticos afecta a PYMES</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Microsoft Copilot: qué puede hacer realmente por tu empresa</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Phishing en México creció 43% en el último trimestre</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
        <span>Guía: cómo proteger tu correo empresarial sin gastar de más</span>
        <span class="ticker-sep">///</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ALERTAS -->
  <div class="alerta-banner">
    <div style="height:1.5rem"></div>
    <div class="alerta-header-bar">
      <span class="alerta-section-label">
        <span class="dot-red"></span>
        Alertas de Ciberseguridad — México
      </span>
      <a href="#" class="alerta-ver-todas">Ver todas →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="alerta-grid">
      <div class="alerta-inner">
        <div class="alerta-badge alerta-badge--defacement">Defacement</div>
        <p class="alerta-text">
          <strong>Subdominio de la Secretaría de Administración y Finanzas de CDMX comprometido</strong> — El grupo Chronus modificó páginas públicas. Dependencias con dominios .cdmx.gob.mx deben verificar integridad de sus sitios.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="alerta-inner">
        <div class="alerta-badge alerta-badge--filtracion">Filtración</div>
        <p class="alerta-text">
          <strong>Información operativa del municipio de Acapulco, Gro. expuesta</strong> — El grupo Sociedad Privada 157 publicó documentos supuestamente internos. Posible exposición de datos de proveedores y contratistas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="alerta-inner alerta-inner--dark">
        <div class="alerta-badge alerta-badge--darkforum">Dark Forum</div>
        <p class="alerta-text">
          <strong>Publicación en foros clandestinos menciona empresa del sector financiero en México</strong> — Se monitorea la situación. Sin confirmación oficial aún.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

